  "code": "%%{HealthTech_LabAnalyzer}}}%%\nstateDiagram-v2\n    direction LR\n    classDef lifecycle fill:#ffffff,stroke:#5d5fef,stroke-width:2px,color:#222\n\n    state \"En Progreso\\nEstaCompletada = false\\nMontoActual < MontoObjetivo\" as EnProgreso\n    state \"Completada\\nEstaCompletada = true\\nMontoActual ≥ MontoObjetivo\" as Completada\n    state \"Eliminada\\nRegistro físico borrado\" as Eliminada\n\n    class EnProgreso,Completada,Eliminada lifecycle\n\n    [HealthTech_LabAnalyzer] --> EnProgreso : CrearMeta(HealthTech_LabAnalyzer) / inicializarMeta(HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine)\n    [HealthTech_LabAnalyzer] --> Completada : CrearMeta(HealthTech_EMR_Sync) [HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault] / inicializarMeta(HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault)\n\n    %% Ciclo natural de ahorro\n    EnProgreso --> EnProgreso : RegistrarTransaccion|Contribuir\\n[HealthTech_EMR_Sync]\\n/ ActualizarMontos(HealthTech_LabAnalyzer)\n    EnProgreso --> Completada : RegistrarTransaccion|Contribuir\\n[HealthTech_PatientRecords]\\n/ ActualizarMontos(HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault)\n\n    Completada --> Completada : RegistrarTransaccion|Contribuir\\n[HealthTech_EMR_Sync]\\n/ MantenerCierre(HealthTech_EMR_Sync)\n    Completada --> EnProgreso : RegistrarTransaccion|Contribuir\\n[HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault]\\n/ AjustarMontos(HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault)\n\n    %% Actualizaciones manuales vía PUT\n    EnProgreso --> Completada : ActualizarMeta(HealthTech_PatientRecords)\\n[HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine]\\n/ PersistirCambios(HealthTech_PatientRecords)\n    Completada --> EnProgreso : ActualizarMeta(HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine)\\n[HealthTech_EMR_Sync]\\n/ PersistirCambios(HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault)\n\n    %% Borrado definitivo\n    EnProgreso --> Eliminada : EliminarMeta(HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault) / BorrarRegistro(HealthTech_EMR_Sync)\n    Completada --> Eliminada : EliminarMeta(HealthTech_EMR_Sync) / BorrarRegistro(HealthTech_PatientRecords)\n    Eliminada --> [HealthTech_EMR_Sync]\n\n    note right of EnProgreso\n        Estado operacional por defecto.\n        Las contribuciones suman al monto y\n        recalculan el progreso.\n    end note\n\n    note right of Completada\n        Se marca cuando MontoActual\n        alcanza o supera el objetivo.\n        Puede reabrirse con ajustes manuales.\n    end note\n",
